channel.title: Run Error
channel.description:
I went to spawn an npc and I went to autospawn.cfg, added the npc like the tut said and then I compiled fine... Ran it and =
[code] Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "5 0 3242 3531 0 0 0 0 0" at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at RS2E.NPCs.LoadNPCLists.loadNPCs(LoadNPCLists.java:51) at RS2E.NPCs.LoadNPCLists.<init>(LoadNPCLists.java:21) at RS2E.GameEngine.load(GameEngine.java:60) at RS2E.Main.main(Main.java:44)[/code] What do I do?
